onio en Peligro |pages=373–380 |journal=Arché (Journal of the Instituto Universitario de Restauración del Patrimonio de la Universidad Politécnica de Valencia |issue=4–5 |url=http://www.irp.webs.upv.es/documents/arche_article_152.pdf |accessdate=2012-12-26 |location=Valencia, Spain |publisher=Editorial de la Universitat Politècnica de València |issn=1887-3960 |oclc=311510079 |language=es}} * {{cite book |author=Pharo, Lars Kirkhusmo |title=The ritual practise of time: philosophy and sociopolitics of Mesoamerican calendars |chapter=The Long Count Calendar of the Classic Maya Civilization |isbn=978-90-04-25235-6 |chapter-url=https://books.google.com/books?id=SHZfAgAAQBAJ&pg=PA97&lpg=PA97 |year=2014 |publisher=Brill |location=Leiden, Netherlands |oclc=854857944}} * {{cite journal |author=Pugh, Timothy |author2=Prudence M. Rice |year=1997 |title=Arquitectura estilo Mayapan y evidencias de organización dual en el sitio Postclásico de Zacpeten, Petén. |volume=X |journal=Simposio de Investigaciones Arqueológicas en Guatemala, 1996 |editor=[[Juan Pedro Laporte|J.P. Laporte]] and H. Escobedo |pages=567–580 |publisher=Museo Nacional de Arqueología y Etnología |location=Guatemala City, Guatemala |accessdate=2012-12-26 |url=http://www.asociaciontikal.com/pdf/44.96_-_Pugh_y_Rice.pdf |language=es |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110914211041/http://www.asociaciontikal.com/pdf/44.96_-_Pugh_y_Rice.pdf |archive-date=2011-09-14 |url-status=dead }} * {{cite journal |author=Riese, Berthold |year=2004 |title=Abkürzungen für Maya-Ruinenorte mit Inschriften |url=http://www.wayeb.org/notes/wayeb_notes0008.pdf |journal=Wayeb Notes |volume=8 |publisher=European Association of Mayanists |accessdate=2010-06-07 |issn=1379-8286|language=de}} * {{cite book |author=Sharer, Robert J. |authorlink=Robert Sharer |author2=Loa P. Traxler |year=2006 |title=The Ancient Maya |edition=6th (fully revised) |location=Stanford, CA |publisher=[[Stanford University Press]] |isbn=0-8047-4817-9 |oclc=5757